import React, {useEffect, useState} from 'react'; import styled from "styled-components"; import { useForm } from "react-hook-form"; import { BrowserRouter, Route, Routes, useParams } from "react-router-dom"; //Styled const Container = styled.div` position: relative; top: 150px; width: 80%; padding-bottom: 40px; `; const SinglePlayer = (props) => { let player = useParams(); const [items, setItems] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { fetch(`/get_single_player_data/${player.id}`) .then((response) => response.json()) .then((data) => setItems(data)) },[player]) const { id, assists_per_game, blocks_per_game, defensive_rebounds_per_game, field_goal_percentage, field_goals_attempted_per_game, field_goals_made_per_game, free_throw_percentage, games_played, minutes_per_game, name, offensive_rebounds_per_game, player_efficiency_rating, points_per_game, rebounds_per_game, steals_per_game, team_acronym, team_name, three_point_attempted_per_game, three_point_made_per_game, three_point_percentage, turnovers_per_game, } = items && items[0]; return (
Player ID {id}
Name {name}
Team {team_acronym}
TeamName {team_name}
Games {games_played}
MPG {minutes_per_game}
FGA {field_goals_attempted_per_game}
FGM {field_goals_made_per_game}
FG% {field_goal_percentage}
FT% {free_throw_percentage}
3PA {three_point_attempted_per_game}
3PM {team_name}
Team {team_name}
Team {team_name}
Team {team_name}
Team {team_name}
Team {team_name}
Team {team_name}
Team {team_name}
Team {team_name}
Team {team_name}
Team {team_name}
) } export default SinglePlayer;
